CRYSTAL APPLIED said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 35.18% to NT$161,342,000 from NT$248,904,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales            161,342          248,904    
YOY%             -35.18%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            505,833          965,862    
YOY%             -47.63% 
=================================================================
 